data.description: Great floorplan! First floor kitchen offering stainless steel appliances, gas stove and lots of counter space. Also on the first floor is a open living area with access to the backyard. This well maintained home has all bedrooms upstairs, the main bedroom has a full bathroom and walk-in closet, this home also has upgraded flooring throughout and is bright and welcoming.
